  "texts": [
    "This includes healthy political commentary and critique.",
    "B: (Bad) Variable referring to the use of GenAI for an ostensibly nefarious purpose, relevant to an election.",
    "This includes Example 1: (G) \"AI-manipulated video of Modi dancing and singing\" \"AI tools utilized to support translation needs for a speech in a rural community\" Example 2: (B) \"AI deepfake of a leading political candidate in a sexualised context\" \"AI deepfake video manipulating a PPC's campaign promise\" \"Bot call attempts at mimicry or deception and disinformation.",
